1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:00,320
Rulan...

3
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:06,840
They're all forcing me.

4
00:01:07,359 --> 00:01:08,159
Rulan.

5
00:01:08,879 --> 00:01:09,719
Rulan.

6
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:12,840
Rulan.

7
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,519
Rulan.

8
00:01:17,319 --> 00:01:18,560
Rulan.

9
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:29,640
Rulan.

10
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,760
(Rulan,)

11
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:38,200
(I was too weak.)

12
00:01:38,879 --> 00:01:40,840
(I didn't stand with you.)

13
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:43,840
(I will avenge you.)

14
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:47,900
(Lin Rulan's Grave)

15
00:01:49,620 --> 00:01:53,100
(Lin Rulan's Grave)

16
00:01:58,239 --> 00:01:59,719
Wan, you still remember

17
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:01,120
we all love chestnut cakes.

18
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:04,120
I'll stay by Wu Lian's side
to send you word.

19
00:02:04,799 --> 00:02:07,680
Step by step, lead him into our trap.

20
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,960
Let him taste

21
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,919
what it's like to be trapped
with no escape.

22
00:02:15,780 --> 00:02:19,700
=Episode 18=

23
00:02:27,439 --> 00:02:28,400
Nanny Du,

24
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:31,520
I feel truly old.

25
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:36,599
Nonsense. You're in your prime.

26
00:02:37,439 --> 00:02:38,840
In my prime?

27
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:42,199
I would never let those two

28
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:44,400
play their games before me.

29
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,639
I was just thinking,

30
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:50,919
since you've seen through
their schemes,

31
00:02:51,199 --> 00:02:53,120
why keep them here?

32
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:55,120
Those two...

33
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:58,840
One is an embroiderer who
preserves my youth,

34
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:02,520
the other is a cousin who helps me
keep the Prince.

35
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,280
If they stay,

36
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,599
they remain useful.

37
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,639
If I send them away,

38
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:10,360
they might cause even greater trouble.

39
00:03:11,599 --> 00:03:13,719
I fear I couldn't explain it
to the Prince.

40
00:03:14,479 --> 00:03:16,280
What about the real Lady Cheng'en?

41
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:19,840
Shen Ruoheng? She refused to come, fine.

42
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:22,479
But sending a maid to impersonate her?

43
00:03:22,639 --> 00:03:25,960
I'm letting that slide.
That's her good fortune.

44
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:28,280
Would she dare confront me?

45
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:29,680
Don't forget,

46
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,240
my late father-in-law

47
00:03:31,759 --> 00:03:34,199
saved her family's lives.

48
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,919
Very true.

49
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:41,159
But I just fear there may be secrets

50
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:42,360
between that girl and Lady Cheng'en.

51
00:03:43,039 --> 00:03:46,280
She's just a girl with a grudge
against Wu Lian.

52
00:03:46,479 --> 00:03:47,599
It doesn't matter.

53
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:50,159
As long as she pleases the Prince,

54
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:53,520
who at my manor would believe her?

55
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:56,840
Her life is mine to decide.

56
00:03:57,719 --> 00:04:00,000
Besides, even if there are secrets,

57
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:02,800
wouldn't she fear implicating
the real Ruoheng?

58
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:06,319
You've thought of everything.

59
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,680
Oh, right.

60
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:10,240
Tell Luoxia to watch Meng Wan.

61
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,039
Let's see

62
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,520
what schemes they can hatch

63
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:16,120
right under my nose.

64
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,279
Yes.

65
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:19,439
Their antics have tired me out.

66
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,959
Now, I want to go out
for some fresh air.

67
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:47,120
Why are you here?

68
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:48,759
Come to gloat?

69
00:04:58,199 --> 00:05:00,759
Wan, I sent the guards away.

70
00:05:02,839 --> 00:05:03,839
You've suffered.

71
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:05,759
We must be careful.

72
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:07,680
Wu Lian is vicious and deceitful.

73
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,319
His hand was never hurt.

74
00:05:09,519 --> 00:05:11,240
All an act for the Princess Consort.

75
00:05:11,279 --> 00:05:13,120
Rulan, don't agree to anything.

76
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,680
If not for me,

77
00:05:15,399 --> 00:05:16,399
you wouldn't be...

78
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:23,000
Three years ago, I thought
you were dead.

79
00:05:23,319 --> 00:05:25,600
The next day, I went to
Yanyu Embroidery House.

80
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:30,079
I begged Wu Lian to take me in,
to work for him,

81
00:05:30,079 --> 00:05:31,240
to be his servant.

82
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:34,879
I only wanted to find proof
that he drove you to your death.

83
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:38,040
Without your secret notes,
risking everything,

84
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,240
helping me in the shadows,

85
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:41,800
and Mr. Liu and the Yehu Gang,

86
00:05:42,279 --> 00:05:43,879
I never would have lasted till today.

87
00:05:44,279 --> 00:05:46,000
Wu Lian has done so much evil,

88
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,199
incurring public outrage.

89
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:50,839
Most of his victims dare not speak.

90
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:52,480
Only you stood up.

91
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:55,399
The day you went to your death,

92
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:57,680
we were too cowardly to speak.

93
00:05:58,079 --> 00:06:01,360
Now, we're risking our lives

94
00:06:01,519 --> 00:06:05,040
to help you and to make up for

95
00:06:05,079 --> 00:06:07,399
the regret of staying silent
three years ago.

96
00:06:08,279 --> 00:06:10,519
I couldn't save you then.

97
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:14,680
This time, I'll die with no regrets.

98
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:15,879
Don't say that.

99
00:06:16,279 --> 00:06:17,879
Mr. Liu is safe now.

100
00:06:18,079 --> 00:06:19,120
In a day or two,

101
00:06:19,199 --> 00:06:20,680
I'll get you out.

102
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:24,040
The list is what matters.

103
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,279
Did Xiaoshou find it?

104
00:06:31,279 --> 00:06:32,600
Why should I respect you?

105
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:35,319
Isn't it enough that you got my master
poisoned and his hand hurt?

106
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,519
Respect you?

107
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:37,759
Let me tell you,

108
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:40,519
my master holds secrets of
every powerful family in the city.

109
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,920
Your fate may not be better than mine.

110
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:45,040
How does it feel to be in prison?

111
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:47,800
Daring to curse the Princess Consort
with a headless pheasant.

112
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,160
When the Prince returns,

113
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:50,439
you're as good as dead.

114
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:52,959
How dare you hit me?

115
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,680
I wanted to see

116
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,800
what you look like now,
you wretched woman.

117
00:06:57,439 --> 00:06:59,079
I'll make sure you can't live

118
00:06:59,279 --> 00:07:00,279
and can't die.

119
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:05,399
Wan, why did you do that?

120
00:07:06,279 --> 00:07:07,079
It's nothing.

121
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:09,439
Without that slap,

122
00:07:09,879 --> 00:07:12,040
how could others believe you?

123
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,279
By the way,

124
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:17,279
look.

125
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:19,279
I accidentally broke it.

126
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:27,720
I remember back then,

127
00:07:28,399 --> 00:07:29,879
you always snuck into the small kitchen

128
00:07:29,879 --> 00:07:31,560
to steal chestnut cakes.

129
00:07:33,759 --> 00:07:34,560
Wan.

130
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:42,959
Look.

131
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:47,120
You stole chestnut cakes again.

132
00:07:47,399 --> 00:07:48,199
Try one.

133
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,240
Master Wu has arrived.

134
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:07,680
How is it?

135
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:10,839
As sweet as before.

136
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,519
Alright.

137
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,439
Go now.

138
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,439
Someone might see.

139
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,319
Wait for me, Wan.

140
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:22,759
I'll get you out.

141
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:24,600
I know.

142
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:25,800
Go.

143
00:08:27,300 --> 00:08:31,020
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

144
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:32,279
Rulan.

145
00:08:36,420 --> 00:08:39,300
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

146
00:08:39,660 --> 00:08:41,660
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

147
00:08:41,660 --> 00:08:45,740
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

148
00:08:46,140 --> 00:08:48,340
♪For your faith that never broke♪

149
00:08:48,540 --> 00:08:52,660
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

150
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:55,460
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

151
00:08:55,460 --> 00:08:59,700
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

152
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:03,420
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

153
00:09:03,540 --> 00:09:06,180
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

154
00:09:06,180 --> 00:09:08,780
♪One thought turns into ash♪

155
00:09:09,740 --> 00:09:15,100
♪No future left to write♪

156
00:09:15,620 --> 00:09:18,020
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

157
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:21,420
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

158
00:09:23,100 --> 00:09:25,300
♪If we meet again someday♪

159
00:09:25,740 --> 00:09:29,780
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪

160
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,159
Be well.

161
00:09:35,639 --> 00:09:36,759
You must be well.

162
00:09:37,679 --> 00:09:38,480
Go.

163
00:09:44,799 --> 00:09:45,600
Wait for me.

164
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:55,759
(Rulan,)

165
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:59,799
(three years ago, I was a coward.
I couldn't save you.)

166
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:02,960
(This time, let me be brave.)

167
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:05,799
(Your path to revenge
is too hard.)

168
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:09,039
(If sacrifice is inevitable,)

169
00:10:09,639 --> 00:10:11,440
(let it be me.)

170
00:10:11,919 --> 00:10:13,600
(Let my life)

171
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:16,399
(be the sharpest blade in your hand.)

172
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,000
(Rulan.)

173
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:22,000
(You must live on)

174
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,559
(for both of us.)

175
00:10:54,540 --> 00:10:57,500
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

176
00:10:57,740 --> 00:11:00,740
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

177
00:11:01,940 --> 00:11:04,700
♪The past no longer binds♪

178
00:11:05,180 --> 00:11:08,900
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

179
00:11:09,340 --> 00:11:13,460
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

180
00:11:14,300 --> 00:11:17,180
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

