00:11:44,020 --> 00:11:46,620
♪One thought turns into ash♪

190
00:11:47,580 --> 00:11:52,940
♪No future left to write♪

191
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:55,820
♪If I never fall♪

192
00:11:55,860 --> 00:11:58,220
♪How could this waiting end♪

193
00:11:58,220 --> 00:11:59,580
♪If I bear no scars♪

194
00:11:59,580 --> 00:12:01,900
♪How could I challenge fate♪

195
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:04,260
♪I knew there was no way back♪

196
